### Set environment variables
@host = http://localhost:8080/api/payments
@authToken = Bearer tu_token_aqui
@paymentId = id_de_tu_pago_aqui
@orderId = id_de_tu_orden_aqui

### 1. Crear nuevo pago (POST)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "customerId": 1,
  "amount": 25000.0,
  "paymentMethod": "EFECTIVO",
  "notes": "Pago de comida"
}

### 2. Obtener todos los pagos (GET)
GET {{host}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 3. Obtener detalle de un pago específico (GET)
GET {{host}}/{{paymentId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
